                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17841208-57-off308 t17841208-57-cd309"></join> last, fifty four yards of silk ribbon, value 20 s. the property of 
                     
                        <persName id="t17841208-57-victim814" type="victimName">
