                  , privately in his shop
            </rs>.</p>
               <p>The prisoner came into the Prosecutor's shop, for some trifling things, and as soon as he went, the shopman missed three pieces of ribbon, he immediately pursued the prisoner, who perceiving him follow him, ran into an entry, and dropped the ribbons on the ground.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t17841208-57-person815">
                  George
                   Mecham
               <interp inst="t17841208-57-person815" type="surname" value="Mecham"></interp>
