            </rs>,</p>
               <p>Court to Prisoner. How old are you? - Thirteen.</p>
               <p>
                  <xptr type="pageFacsimile" doc="178412080128"></xptr>Court to Prisoner. You have began very early to lead a dishonest life, it is to be hoped this will be a warning to you, think that you may have a long life, to live and make up for what you have done. - Let him be <rs id="t17841208-57-punish311" type="punishmentDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17841208-57-punish311" type="punishmentCategory" value="miscPunish"></interp>
